# Project overview

**Repo:** SMS (OPS Platform internal management). **Monolith:** Laravel 13 + Inertia.js + Vue 3 (not separate BE/FE repos).

## Stack

- **PHP:** ^8.3 · **Laravel** 13 · Sanctum · Breeze · Ziggy
- **FE:** Vue 3 (Composition API) · Vite · Tailwind · pages under `resources/js/`
- **Tests:** PHPUnit (SQLite in-memory via `phpunit.xml`)
- **Docs:** `docs/` · **Plans:** `plans/` (see `plans/ops-platform-brief.md`)

## Functional modules (target)

Resources, Websites, Projects/Kanban, Knowledge CMS, Team/RBAC, Contracts, AI accounts, OKRs — details in `plans/ops-platform-brief.md`.

## Directory map

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `app/` | Models, HTTP (Controllers, Middleware, Form Requests), Providers |
| `routes/web.php`, `routes/auth.php` | Web + Inertia routes |
| `database/migrations`, `database/seeders` | Schema & seeds |
| `resources/js/` | Vue pages, layouts, components (`@/` → `resources/js/`) |
| `resources/views/app.blade.php` | Inertia root |
| `tests/` | Feature & Unit tests |

## Agent behavior

- Match existing Laravel Breeze/Inertia patterns before introducing new libraries.
- API responses must follow ISC envelope (see `04-api-response.mdc`).
- Commits: `type(scope): description [AI]` ≤ 72 chars (see `03-commit-convention.mdc`).
- Never commit `.env`, secrets, or log PII.
